Introduction

Cheong Eum is a South Korean singer under W2 Company. She is set to debut as a member of the girl group Bunny.T in June 2023.

In 2019, Cheong Eum debuted as a member of the girl group API. However, after years of inactivity, it is presumed that API had disbanded.
